  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 1st level, as an action you can mold your chakra into steel to create a <em>Steel Weapon</em>. You can create any weapon that you have seen before and that is made from a metal source. All Steel Weapons have the Returning, Thrown, and Finesse properties to you and use the damage die of the weapon they resemble. You are proficient with all weapons you conjure with this latent.</p>",
